    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several minor dings, some paint fading on the hood, and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, although it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
